Map, made by ME!

Had an idea of a aim_ag_texture map, but it accidentally came as fun_ map, cause theres NO aiming skills needed. (No long distances/small holes etc.) Too lazy to change the name :P

I think that the map is pretty good looking, even I finished it in a hurry, out of the way for my brilliant idea in the next map. 
The map is symmetric, and theres a SECRET ROOM.

-Buyzone
-secret room
-24 Spawns (12 Each, not sure maybe more or less ;D)
